<tree text="2. Dasasikkh&#x101;pada&#x1E43;" target="text">
  <text>
    <paragraph nr="1"> Pāṇātipātā veramaṇī-sikkhāpadaṃ <note>[veramaṇīsikkhāpadaṃ (sī. syā.)]</note> samādiyāmi.</paragraph>
    <paragraph nr="2"> Adinnādānā veramaṇī-sikkhāpadaṃ samādiyāmi.</paragraph>
    <paragraph nr="3"> Abrahmacariyā  veramaṇī-sikkhāpadaṃ samādiyāmi.</paragraph>
    <paragraph nr="4"> Musāvādā veramaṇī-sikkhāpadaṃ samādiyāmi.</paragraph>
    <paragraph nr="5"> Surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānā veramaṇī-sikkhāpadaṃ samādiyāmi .</paragraph>
    <paragraph nr="6"> Vikālabhojanā veramaṇī-sikkhāpadaṃ samādiyāmi.</paragraph>
    <paragraph nr="7"> Nacca-gīta-vādita-visūkadassanā veramaṇī-sikkhāpadaṃ samādiyāmi.</paragraph>
    <paragraph nr="8"> Mālā-gandha-vilepana-dhāraṇa-maṇḍana-vibhūsanaṭṭhānā veramaṇī-sikkhāpadaṃ samādiyāmi.</paragraph>
    <paragraph nr="9"> Uccāsayana-mahāsayanā veramaṇī-sikkhāpadaṃ samādiyāmi.</paragraph>
    <paragraph nr="10"> Jātarūpa-rajatapaṭiggahaṇā  veramaṇī-sikkhāpadaṃ samādiyāmi.</paragraph>
    <centered>Dasasikkhāpadaṃ <note>[dasasikkhāpadaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ (syā.)]</note> niṭṭhitaṃ.</centered>
  </text>
</tree>
